snippet.title: Mike Dies Trailer
snippet.description:
A New Breed of Metroidvania

Mike Dies is a challenging fast-paced platformer with dynamic brutal fatalities and a massive non-linear environment.

Available on Steam February 23rd 2018:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/696200/Mike_Dies/
